thread.title: J&J Pallet Solutions
thread.title_full: FolderPrinters.com reviewed by J&J Pallet Solutions

author: J&J Pallet Solutions
title: J&J Pallet Solutions
text: I was in search of a company to print our new sales brochures. FolderPrinters.com was fantastic! They had a great turn around time, decent pricing, easy to use template, and their customer service can't be beat. Although my design was already figured out the customer service team proofed my file before sending to print the hard copy proof. It was perfect on the 1st go! We will definitely be reordering with them!
